---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="py-24" id="workflow-timeline">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Option Label -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <span class="inline-block bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Opción 2 — Workflow</span>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Un día con Dokos</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Una sola app que te acompaña desde la primera taza de café hasta el último commit del día.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Vertical line -->
      <div class="absolute left-6 sm:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/50 via-yellow-500/50 via-green-500/50 to-purple-500/50 hidden sm:block" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="absolute left-6 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/50 via-yellow-500/50 via-green-500/50 to-purple-500/50 sm:hidden" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 — Morning -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <div class="sm:w-1/2 sm:text-right sm:pr-8 pl-16 sm:pl-0">
          <span class="text-xs text-primary font-mono font-bold">09:00</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1">Revisas un PR</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Abres el diff de una configuración YAML. Ves los cambios lado a lado, sin abrir el IDE.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-3 sm:left-1/2 sm:-translate-x-1/2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary/20 border-2 border-primary flex items-center justify-center z-10">
          <Icon name="difference" size="text-sm" class="text-primary" />
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:block sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-8">
          <div class="bg-surface-dark border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="text-[9px] bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 px-1.5 rounded">- timeout: 30</span>
              <span class="text-[9px] bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 px-1.5 rounded">+ timeout: 60</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded w-full mb-1"></div>
            <div class="h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded w-3/4"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 — Mid morning -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <div class="hidden sm:block sm:w-1/2 sm:pr-8 sm:text-right">
          <div class="bg-surface-dark border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-3">
            <div class="flex justify-end gap-1 mb-2">
              <div class="h-6 w-12 bg-primary/15 rounded border border-primary/25 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-[7px] text-primary">A</span>
              </div>
              <span class="text-slate-600 text-xs">→</span>
              <div class="h-6 w-12 bg-yellow-500/15 rounded border border-yellow-500/25 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-[7px] text-yellow-400">B</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded w-full mb-1"></div>
            <div class="h-1.5 bg-primary/20 rounded w-2/3 ml-auto"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-3 sm:left-1/2 sm:-translate-x-1/2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/20 border-2 border-yellow-500 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
          <Icon name="edit_note" size="text-sm" class="text-yellow-400" />
        </div>
        <div class="sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-8 pl-16">
          <span class="text-xs text-yellow-400 font-mono font-bold">11:00</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1">Escribes documentación</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Editas un Markdown con diagramas Mermaid y fórmulas LaTeX. Todo se renderiza en el split view.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 — Afternoon -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <div class="sm:w-1/2 sm:text-right sm:pr-8 pl-16 sm:pl-0">
          <span class="text-xs text-green-400 font-mono font-bold">14:30</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1">Analizas un dataset</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Un CSV de 50,000 filas. Ordenas, filtras y buscas sin esperar que Excel abra.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-3 sm:left-1/2 sm:-translate-x-1/2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 border-2 border-green-500 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
          <Icon name="table_chart" size="text-sm" class="text-green-400" />
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:block sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-8">
          <div class="bg-surface-dark border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-3">
            <div class="flex gap-1 mb-2">
              <div class="h-1.5 flex-1 bg-green-500/30 rounded"></div>
              <div class="h-1.5 flex-1 bg-green-500/30 rounded"></div>
              <div class="h-1.5 flex-1 bg-green-500/30 rounded"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div></div>
              <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div></div>
              <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-green-500/15 rounded"></div><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div><div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 — Late afternoon -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <div class="hidden sm:block sm:w-1/2 sm:pr-8 sm:text-right">
          <div class="bg-surface-dark border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-3">
            <div class="space-y-1 mb-2">
              <div class="h-1.5 bg-red-500/30 rounded w-full"></div>
              <div class="h-1.5 bg-yellow-500/20 rounded w-4/5"></div>
              <div class="h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded w-full"></div>
              <div class="h-1.5 bg-red-500/30 rounded w-3/4"></div>
              <div class="h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded w-full"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-3 sm:left-1/2 sm:-translate-x-1/2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 border-2 border-red-500 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
          <Icon name="bug_report" size="text-sm" class="text-red-400" />
        </div>
        <div class="sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-8 pl-16">
          <span class="text-xs text-red-400 font-mono font-bold">16:00</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1">Debuggeas un error</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Abres un log de 200MB. Los errores se colorean automáticamente. Filtras por severidad y encuentras el bug en segundos.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 — Evening -->
      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8">
        <div class="sm:w-1/2 sm:text-right sm:pr-8 pl-16 sm:pl-0">
          <span class="text-xs text-purple-400 font-mono font-bold">17:30</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1">Verificas la API</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1">Abres el spec OpenAPI y pruebas los endpoints directamente con el Swagger UI integrado. Sin salir de Dokos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-3 sm:left-1/2 sm:-translate-x-1/2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 border-2 border-purple-500 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
          <Icon name="api" size="text-sm" class="text-purple-400" />
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:block sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-8">
          <div class="bg-surface-dark border border-slate-800 rounded-lg p-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="text-[9px] bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 px-1.5 rounded font-mono">GET</span>
              <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-mono">/api/v1/users</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-[9px] bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 px-1.5 rounded font-mono">POST</span>
              <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-mono">/api/v1/deploy</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom tagline -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">5 tareas. 5 tipos de archivo. <span class="text-white font-medium">Una sola app.</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
